name: Aurra Sing (V)
Lore: 'Bounty hunter. Former student of the Force. After failing her Jedi training, Aurra became known for hunting down and killing Jedi Knights.',
Text: 'Once during opponent''s activate phase, may relocate Aurra to a site where opponent has a Jedi. Once per game, during your move phase, may fire her weapon at a Jedi; hit target is lost. Immune to attrition < 4.(Original concept by Sam Tashima - North Dakota States 2005)',
